                            <comment id="17760474" author="svorc" created="Wed, 30 Aug 2023 14:47:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This also affects CXF 4.x branch. We had to use the &quot;force.urlconnection.http.conduit&quot; property in all our CXF clients, otherwise the threads quickly get deadlocked, one for every remote service connection error.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17762562" author="JIRAUSER301091" created="Thu, 7 Sep 2023 04:16:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dkulp&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dkulp&quot;&gt;dkulp&lt;/a&gt; ,&lt;/p&gt;

