&lt;p&gt;you resolved this issue and marked that it&apos;s resolved with &lt;tt&gt;3.6.1&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;4.0.2&lt;/tt&gt;, but this issue affects versions &lt;tt&gt;3.6.1&lt;/tt&gt; (the actual version I tested). I think that&apos;s not correct.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Furthermore, I can&apos;t find a reference in the &lt;tt&gt;4.0.2&lt;/tt&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cxf/compare/cxf-4.0.1...cxf-4.0.2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;release&lt;/a&gt; to this ticket. Which commit fixed it?&lt;/p&gt;

